---
import { Linkedin } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-8">
  <!-- Header section with image, title, and subtitle -->
  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-6 mb-8">
    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
      <img
        src="https://github.com/jorgeteixe.png"
        alt="Jorge Teixeira"
        class="w-24 h-24 sm:w-28 sm:h-28 rounded-full border-2 border-gray-200"
      />
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex-1">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          Jorge Teixeira
        </h1>
        <a
          href="https://linkedin.com/in/jorge-teixeira-crespo"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="p-2 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          aria-label="LinkedIn Profile"
        >
          <Linkedin size={20} />
        </a>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600">
        Breaking Computers & Other Stuff
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Full-width intro paragraph -->
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      I enjoy solving problems and building things. From full stack apps to
      Kubernetes infrastructure, from organizing events to playing guitar — I
      dive into challenges and learn what's needed. Below you'll find the story of what brought me to who I am today — not a deep technical overview, but the high-level journey through the experiences that shaped my path.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
